题比以往任何时候都更容易，在这种情况下，通常会滥用特权。</p><p>在谈到专辑中的新曲目时，Vega说：“这是您在民主中不想要的事情：关闭了人们会发言权的扬声器角落。这是人们说很多话的时刻，但有时他们没有有意义或没有说实话。人们应该对自己说的话负责。他们不能只是撒谎。人们会认为那是不言而喻的。”</p><p>在下面听。 </p><p><iframe title="Suzanne Vega-扬声器角（官方抒情视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IejCc2s6zQk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>为了纪念她的新专辑“与天使的飞行”的发行，Vega还宣布了一次巡回演出，该巡回演出将在利物浦，剑桥，斯托克和布里斯托尔等城市停留。这次旅行将在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅结束。嘉宾凯瑟琳·普里迪（Katherine Priddy）将参加这些节目。</p><p>门票将于3月7日上午10点开始销售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsuzanne-vega-tickets%2Fartist%2F736386">在这里</a>获得。</p><h2><strong>苏珊·维加（Suzanne Vega）的2025年英国巡演日期是：</strong></h2><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>19盖茨黑德，圣人盖茨黑德</strong><br /><strong>曼彻斯特20号，布里奇沃特大厅</strong><br /><strong>21格拉斯哥，皇家音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>23爱丁堡，乌瑟尔大厅</strong><br /><strong>25利物浦，皇家利物浦爱乐乐团</strong><br /><strong>27剑桥，玉米交换</strong><strong> </strong><br /><strong>28布莱顿，圆顶</strong><br /><strong>30布里斯托尔，布里斯托尔灯塔</strong><br /><strong>31伯明翰，交响乐大厅</strong></p><p><strong>十一月</strong><br /><strong>1史克，摄政剧院</strong><br /><strong>3伦敦，皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suzanne-vega-announces-first-album-in-over-a-decade-flying-with-angels-with-thought-provoking-single-speakers-corner-3843617">苏珊·维加（Suzanne Vega）邮报宣布了十多年的第一张专辑，即“与天使的飞行”，发人深省的单曲“扬声器角”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
听朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas） + voidz的“未来派新单曲“蓝色恶魔” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-julian-casablancas-the-voidz-futuristic-new-new-single-new-single-blue-demon-3843628?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = listo to to-julian-casablancas-the-voidz-futuristic-futuristic-new-new-single-single-blue-demonAnagricel Duran Tue, 04 Mar 2025 21:52:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsExperimentalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3843628 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Voidz的Julian Casablancas在Primavera Sound Madrid 2023。（Mariano Regidor/Redferns摄" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该曲目是乐队即将到来的EP的第一个品尝者，该曲目将于今年春季晚些时候发布</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-julian-casablancas-the-voidz-futuristic-new-single-blue-demon-3843628">听朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas） + voidz的“未来派新单曲“蓝色恶魔”（New Demon）</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Voidz的Julian Casablancas在Primavera Sound Madrid 2023。（Mariano Regidor/Redferns摄" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Voidz-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Julian-Casablancas">朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas）</a> + <a href="/artists/The-Voidz">voidz</a>从即将到来的EP中分享了他们未来派的新单曲“蓝色恶魔”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/julian-casablancas-interview-the-voidz-like-all-before-you-album-3795205">朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯（Julian Casablancas）将世界设定为权利：“我们总是认为我们如此特别，超越了旧的方式，但我们不是”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该曲目以Voidz的签名合成器较重的实验节拍以及Casablancas的自动调节重型人声演唱：<br />我们互相战斗 /像两个兄弟 /父亲一样，原谅我起义 /太多的婴儿 /像母亲一样死了，”描述了一场冲突。</p><p> “蓝色恶魔”在乐队的官方Instagram帐户上被取笑，并由AI创建了几个帖子。第一个剪辑看到一位新闻记者阅读了乐队的“前社交媒体经理” Tron Cole的来信，他威胁要泄露乐队的新音乐。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="voidz-蓝色恶魔（歌词）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WEZJpFXKTPk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>根据新闻稿，该曲目是Voidz即将发行的EP的第一个品尝器，该曲目将于今年春季晚些时候发布。 “ Blue Demon”是乐队发行的第一首新音乐，其第三张和最新专辑《 2024年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-you-release-atmospheric-opener-overture-3772961#:~:text=In%20a%20four%2Dstar%20review,as%20part%20of%20The%20Strokes.">“像之前”</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，Voidz <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julian-casablancas-the-voidz-announce-2025-london-show-buy-tickets-3818774">将于明天（3月5日）在巴黎的Les Inrocks音乐节上演出，并于3月8日（3月8日）在Troxy举行的伦敦举行的一次演出</a>。这两种出现以前都被称为“两晚混乱和超越”。</p><p>它补充说：“这些即将到来的表现有望提供Voidz的标志性融合，具有无情的能量，反对流派的音景以及令人着迷的表演，这些表演已成为他们现场体验的标志。”两场音乐会都将以尚未宣布的特别嘉宾为特色。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGgDU3SOn_q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.